replies.body:
Thanks for the laughs everyone who came along to Fridays Customs night, that was way funnier than I thought it was going to be.
MVP for the night was DJBearfy with an awesome +75 score. Gratz! {{summoner:30}}

Also, welcome to DSA for DJBearfy, Son of the Bong, and BurstFire301. Good times all. :D

So Donger Dash was a raging success. People seemed to be using some form of teamwork for some reason. :P

MVP for the night was Vigour who came 1st in 4 games, 14 score total, followed by Pathway with 2 1st's for the night, and 11 score. GJ guys, way to leave me behind. {{summoner:6}} 

We had a record number of people on Teamspeak on Friday and Saturday, and had to request extra channels. Good to see all the new blood coming in.

**Friday night EVENTS NIGHT** @ 7pm Sydney time - This week: _Ultimate Bravery mode._

Join us on teamspeak for some tomfoolery.
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}

Welcome to DSA for Pathway, Cirno, Leviathan, Pandorica/Gloomies and Lucky. Good to have you guys aboard.

Don't forget to jump on tonight at 7pm Sydney time for our customs Ultimate Bravery event, and get your mitts on those precious points!
